Levitate.help: You send a single target violently into the air before slamming them to the ground for smashing damage. The target is also rendered unable to fly for a short while.

Dominate.help: You painfully tear at the mind of a single foe, causing psionic damage and rendering the target helpless, lost in their own mind and unable to defend themselves.

Confuse.help: You invoke confusion in a single target, causing them to be unable to reliably distinguish friend and foe for a short time.

Terrify.help: This power Terrifies foes within a cone area in front of you, causing them to tremble in Fear uncontrollably. The affect is so frightening and overwhelming, that the target takes real damage from the physiological response to this Psionic attack. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Slow
